I have a User class with a contactOptions property. ContactOption conforms to my KeyValueField protocol which looks as follows:
``` objc
@protocol KeyValueField 
@property (nonatomic, strong) id keyProperty;
@property (nonatomic, strong) id valueProperty;
/// returns a NSDictionary used to configure a FXFormField
- (NSDictionary *)keyField;
@end
```
I then have a KeyValueCell that's able to display and bind to these properties.
The actual implementation is a bit cobbled together, but in theory this should allow for a very flexible KeyValueCell.
