@nicklockwood A lot of static consts are private, as well as C functions. Examples:
static const CGFloat FXFormFieldMinLabelWidth = 97;
static inline CGFloat FXFormLabelMinFontSize(UILabel *label)
{
    // ...
}
Those, among others, are used in the implementation of FXFormTextFieldCell. So Copying the implementation as is won't work. The private stuff needs to be replaced.
. Also, some private properties of FXFormField are used (valueClass) and other stuff that I didn't have time to look into, like nextCell.
